# 🗂️ Personal Tabs Dashboard

A simple personal homepage built to organize frequently used websites and tools in one place for quick access.

---

## 🚀 Purpose

This project is designed as a personal productivity hub to reduce time spent searching for commonly used websites and services.

---

## 📁 Categories

- **Utilities** – Development and productivity tools  
- **Social** – Communication and social platforms  
- **Web Editors** – Design and website tools  
- **My Websites** – Personal projects and builds  

---

## 🛠️ Built With

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

---

## 💡 Features

- Organized quick-access tabs
- Clean categorized layout
- Lightweight and fast
- Fully browser-based (no backend)

---

## 👨‍💻 Use Case

Serves as a personal start page for daily browsing and workflow optimization.

---

## 📌 Note

This is a personal utility project and is continuously updated based on user workflow.